.Xr X509_new 3 ,
.Xr X509_sign 3 ,
.Xr X509_VAL_new 3 ,
.Xr X509_verify_cert 3
.Sh HISTORY
These functions first appeared in OpenSSL 1.1.0
and have been available since
.Ox 6.3 .
